mongod --dbpath=<specify the data folder location>

mongoimport --db dataset --collection customer --file <specify the customer json file location with the file name>

mongoimport --db dataset --collection film --file <specify the film json file location with the file name>

connect to the mongodb using following command
    mongo
   
list the database using following command 
	show dbs

select the database using following command
	use <database name>
	
list the collection using following command
	show collections